code: @Override public void addCallback(ListenableFutureCallback<? super T> callback) {     this.callbacks.addCallback(callback). }

@Override public void addCallback(SuccessCallback<? super T> successCallback, FailureCallback failureCallback) {     this.callbacks.addSuccessCallback(successCallback).     this.callbacks.addFailureCallback(failureCallback). }
@Override public T get() throws InterruptedException, ExecutionException {     return this.completableFuture.get(). }
@Override public T get(long timeout, TimeUnit unit) throws InterruptedException, ExecutionException, TimeoutException {     return this.completableFuture.get(timeout, unit). }
